              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SISD",
                "SISD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Five strip telescopes (S1-S5) of Si",
                "strip detectors placed side by side covering a total",
                "angular range of ~93 degree have been used inside a",
                "1.5-m-diameter scattering chamber were used to detect",
                "different breakup fragments in coincidence.",
                "Each strip telescope consists of two Si strip detectors",
                "with thicknesses of ~ 60 um as delta E and ~ 1500 um as",
                "E respectively.",
                "Each detector has 16 vertical and 16 horizontal strips",
                "covering an active area of 50 mm x 50 mm."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two Si-surface barrier detectors of thickness",
                "~1000 um were placed at +/- 20 degree with respect to",
                "beam direction for normalization and beam monitoring."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SIBAR",
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Five telescope (T1-T5) of silicon",
                "surface barrier detectors with delta E ~ 50 um and",
                "E ~ 1000-2000 um thick to measure elastic scattering",
                "angular distribution."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The corrected beam energy with the loss in half target",
                "thickness is ~29.8 MeV (Ec.m./Vb ~ 1.37)."
